 of sorts that he should singularly fail in the most simple of orders.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If anything were to happen to this whole enterprise, this majestic war footing,
 this Holy Campaign, issued by the Gods, commanded by the Castigator himself,
 then it would not be because a lowly clerk or young lieutenant forgot to
 sent out some matériel requisition form, or a call-to-arms teller.
