 keeping him out of focus, making his thoughts and hopes stray from the
 one true path he was now walking, the path of God.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Perhaps indeed the archenemies were lurking around, their malignancy somehow
 trying to veer him away from his newly found purpose, driving him to dark
 corners of his mind he did not wish to revisit.
 Perhaps, it was simply himself, still trying to come to terms with his
 new identity as a believer, not an avaricious atavist, a cold-blooded killer,
 a man seeking to empower himself with unsurpassed might and hidden knowledge,
