\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Pilgrim was unperturbed by such a statement.
 His face was serene, calm to the point of being impassive.
 He replied with a smile:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

