\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

So, tomorrow we will reach His City?
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Pilgrim spoke no more, and silently closed his eyes, and laid himself
 down to sleep, the lukewarm sand's embrace his body's only comfort.
